Revision history for DateTime-Event-Predict

0.01_05

	Bugs fixed:
	 - DTP::Profile now makes sure at least one bucket name is provided if no default profile
	   is set.
	
	Changes:
	 - Buckets in a DTP object are actual DTP::Profile::Bucket objects now
	
	Features added:
	 - Added _generate_bucket_statistics() method that will take the mean, stdev and variance
	   from _bucket_statistics and stick them in the bucket(s) automatically
	 - Added _cluster_dates() which takes a list of dates and returns them in clusters

0.01_04 2010-01-31 00:21:22
	
	Bug fixed:
	 - Fixed test in t/09-today.t failing when the current day was at end of month

